#: includes/admin-settings.php
msgid "When enabled, the plugin records anonymous usage statistics (provider, model, latency, errors) and saves chat conversations in your site database. The Statistics and History admin tabs appear. Disabled by default; nothing is stored until you turn this on. Disabling stops new collection; existing records remain until you delete them or uninstall the plugin."
